eeprom_lock.description: EEPROM values can only be modified when Torque Enable (address 64) is set to 0.

fields.name: Model Number
fields.description: Model identification number.

fields.name: Model Information
fields.description: Model information.

fields.name: Firmware Version
fields.description: Firmware version.

fields.name: ID
fields.description: Unique servo ID on the bus.

fields.name: Baud Rate
fields.description: Communication baud rate.

fields.name: Return Delay Time
fields.description: Delay time before Status Packet is returned after receiving an Instruction Packet.

fields.name: Drive Mode
fields.description: Configures drive direction, profile type, and torque-on behavior.

fields.name: Operating Mode
fields.description: Sets the operating mode of the servo.

fields.name: Secondary ID
fields.description: Secondary ID for group control. 255 disables secondary ID.

fields.name: Protocol Type
fields.description: Dynamixel protocol version.

fields.name: Homing Offset
fields.description: Adjusts the home position. The offset is added to Present Position.

fields.name: Moving Threshold
fields.description: Velocity threshold to determine whether the servo is in motion. Moving(122) is set to 1 when velocity exceeds this value.

fields.name: Temperature Limit
fields.description: Maximum internal temperature limit. Exceeding this triggers a Shutdown if configured.

fields.name: Max Voltage Limit
fields.description: Maximum allowed input voltage.

fields.name: Min Voltage Limit
fields.description: Minimum allowed input voltage.

fields.name: PWM Limit
fields.description: Maximum PWM output limit.

fields.name: Velocity Limit
fields.description: Maximum velocity limit.

fields.name: Max Position Limit
fields.description: Maximum position limit for Position Control mode.

fields.name: Min Position Limit
fields.description: Minimum position limit for Position Control mode.

fields.name: Startup Configuration
fields.description: Configures startup behavior for torque and RAM restoration.

values.1: Restore RAM from backup at startup

fields.name: Shutdown
fields.description: Configures which error conditions cause a torque shutdown. Default (52) enables Overheating, Electrical Shock, and Overload errors.

fields.name: Torque Enable
fields.description: Enables/disables motor torque. EEPROM values can only be changed when this is 0.

fields.name: LED
fields.description: Turns the LED on or off.

fields.name: Status Return Level
fields.description: Determines when Status Packets are returned.

fields.name: Registered Instruction
fields.description: Indicates if a REG_WRITE instruction is registered and waiting for ACTION.

fields.name: Hardware Error Status
fields.description: Indicates hardware error conditions. Bit flags match Shutdown(63) configuration.

fields.name: Velocity I Gain
fields.description: Integral gain for velocity control PID.

fields.name: Velocity P Gain
fields.description: Proportional gain for velocity control PID.

fields.name: Position D Gain
fields.description: Derivative gain for position control PID.

fields.name: Position I Gain
fields.description: Integral gain for position control PID.

fields.name: Position P Gain
fields.description: Proportional gain for position control PID.

fields.name: Feedforward 2nd Gain
fields.description: Second feedforward gain for improving trajectory tracking.

fields.name: Feedforward 1st Gain
fields.description: First feedforward gain for improving trajectory tracking.

fields.name: Bus Watchdog
fields.description: Watchdog timer for communication timeout. 0 disables. 1-127 sets timeout interval. Value of -1 indicates watchdog error occurred.

fields.name: Goal PWM
fields.description: Target PWM output value.

fields.name: Goal Velocity
fields.description: Target velocity for Velocity Control mode.

fields.name: Profile Acceleration
fields.description: Acceleration for profile trajectory. Unit depends on Drive Mode: velocity-based = 214.577 rev/min^2, time-based = 1 msec.

fields.name: Profile Velocity
fields.description: Velocity for profile trajectory. In time-based mode, unit is 1 msec.

fields.name: Goal Position
fields.description: Target position. Range is bounded by Min Position Limit(52) and Max Position Limit(48). In Extended Position mode, range is -1,048,575 to 1,048,575.

fields.name: Realtime Tick
fields.description: Time elapsed in milliseconds since the servo powered on. Wraps at 32,767.

fields.name: Moving
fields.description: Indicates whether the servo is in motion (velocity exceeds Moving Threshold).

fields.name: Moving Status
fields.description: Detailed motion status flags indicating profile and in-position state.

fields.name: Present PWM
fields.description: Current PWM output value.

fields.name: Present Load
fields.description: Current load on the motor as a percentage of maximum torque.

fields.name: Present Velocity
fields.description: Current velocity of the motor.

fields.name: Present Position
fields.description: Current position of the motor.

fields.name: Velocity Trajectory
fields.description: Target velocity computed by the profile generator.

fields.name: Position Trajectory
fields.description: Target position computed by the profile generator.

fields.name: Present Input Voltage
fields.description: Current input voltage.

fields.name: Present Temperature
fields.description: Current internal temperature.

fields.name: Backup Ready
fields.description: Indicates if the control table backup is ready for restoration.
